Industry Composition in Seattle (2000)

Source: R/seattle2.R
seattle2.Rd

Business data for the Seattle-Tacoma-Bellevue Metropolitan Statistical Area, Washington (1998 and 2001).

seattle2

Examples

  library(sf)
  data(seattle2)
  plot(seattle2["INFO98"])
}
